{"id":15,"date":"2021-10-16T16:38:21","date_gmt":"2021-10-16T16:38:21","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/amherstgroup.wpengine.com\/?page_id=15"},"modified":"2024-11-07T01:24:34","modified_gmt":"2024-11-07T01:24:34","slug":"home","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/","title":{"rendered":"Home"},"content":{"rendered":"<section id=\"home-hero-block_9c8c9a6b404cb30a10ebe09630b6d9fc\" class=\"home-hero\"><div class=\"home-hero__inner\"><div class=\"home-hero__gallery-wrapper\"><figure class=\"home-hero__gallery\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"home-hero__gallery__image\" src=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/home-hero@2x-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Amherst analyst reviewing housing data with team\" \/><\/figure><\/div><div class=\"home-hero__overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"home-hero__text\"><div class=\"home-hero__text__inner\"><h1 class=\"home-hero__headline\">We are on a mission <br \/><em> to reimagine real estate <\/em><\/h1><\/div><\/div><div class=\"home-hero__bottom\"><svg class=\"home-hero__shape\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1601 38.93\"><path d=\"M0,38.93C175.14,16.35,463,0,788.5,0c340.81,0,640.42,14.53,812.5,38.93Z\"\/><\/svg><button class=\"home-hero__button\" aria-label=\"Scroll to next section\"><svg class=\"home-hero__button__arrow\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 31.113 16.971\"><g transform=\"translate(23.335 -1137.735) rotate(45)\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"2\" transform=\"translate(789 820)\"\/><rect width=\"22\" height=\"2\" transform=\"translate(811 800) rotate(90)\"\/><\/g><\/svg><\/button><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n<div id=\"into\" class=\"block bg-home-intro-gradient block--reduced-top-padding\"><div class=\"block__inner\">\n<style>@media screen and (min-width: 1440px) { \r#single-column-block_434e0cb12b1e746fe5e9ec251258543c .single-column__inner {grid-column: 4 \/ span 6 ;}\r }<\/style><div id=\"single-column-block_434e0cb12b1e746fe5e9ec251258543c\" class=\"single-column\"><div class=\"single-column__inner\">\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Amherst is a vertically integrated real estate investment, development, and operating platform that aims to reimagine some of the most fragmented and inefficient pockets of U.S. real estate, including single-family residential, mortgage-backed securities, and commercial real estate. Fueled by proprietary technology, deep-rooted expertise and an agile, collaborative approach, Amherst is transforming a slow-to-evolve industry by creating innovative solutions that disrupt the real estate ecosystem from end-to-end and unlocks long-term value for the investors, residents and communities it serves.<\/p>\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer hide-on-mobile\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div id=\"hover-card-block_09161577c49a3387a06aa70bc0447932\" class=\"hover-card\"><figure class=\"hover-card__figure\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"856\" height=\"854\" src=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/data-driven@2x.jpg\" class=\"hover-card__figure__image\" alt=\"Two Amherst team members analyzing data\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/data-driven@2x.jpg 856w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/data-driven@2x-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/data-driven@2x-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/data-driven@2x-768x766.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 856px) 100vw, 856px\" \/><div class=\"hover-card__duotone\"><\/div><div class=\"hover-card__overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"hover-card__gradient\"><\/div><\/figure><div class=\"hover-card__arrow\"><svg class=\"hover-card__arrow__image\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 18.938 10.992\"><path d=\"M25.859,20.328l-5.5,5.5V21.336H6.922V19.309H20.363l.012-4.477Z\" transform=\"translate(-6.921 -14.832)\"\/><\/svg><\/div><div class=\"hover-card__front\"><h2 class=\"hover-card__title\">Data Driven<\/h2><h3 class=\"hover-card__subtitle\">Foresight fueled by robust data and proprietary analytics<\/h3><p class=\"hover-card__description\">We have spent decades gathering hundreds of data points on millions of assets, and our proprietary analytical models allow us to spot patterns and anticipate asset behavior as market conditions change. Our team of experts combines these insights with our collective experience to develop data-driven strategies. We have invested $100 million over the past five years to ensure we capture and use data across key decision points. <\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div id=\"hover-card-block_31c5fcdee2a85620ebd87d2a70fe665b\" class=\"hover-card\"><figure class=\"hover-card__figure\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"856\" height=\"854\" src=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/vertically-integrated@2x.jpg\" class=\"hover-card__figure__image\" alt=\"Front of house\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/vertically-integrated@2x.jpg 856w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/vertically-integrated@2x-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/vertically-integrated@2x-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/vertically-integrated@2x-768x766.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 856px) 100vw, 856px\" \/><div class=\"hover-card__duotone\"><\/div><div class=\"hover-card__overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"hover-card__gradient\"><\/div><\/figure><div class=\"hover-card__arrow\"><svg class=\"hover-card__arrow__image\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 18.938 10.992\"><path d=\"M25.859,20.328l-5.5,5.5V21.336H6.922V19.309H20.363l.012-4.477Z\" transform=\"translate(-6.921 -14.832)\"\/><\/svg><\/div><div class=\"hover-card__front\"><h2 class=\"hover-card__title\">Vertically Integrated<\/h2><h3 class=\"hover-card__subtitle\">Efficiency through alignment across in-house services<\/h3><p class=\"hover-card__description\">Amherst is a one-stop offering with everything needed to acquire, finance, manage, and operate residential and commercial real estate. Our vertically integrated services benefit each asset with efficiencies and economies of scale. As a result, we believe property is worth more on our platform. By managing each step in the process, we deliver convenience and value to residents and investors across our businesses. <\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div id=\"hover-card-block_ebce98b03b42ea7211b27ed46fd42220\" class=\"hover-card\"><figure class=\"hover-card__figure\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"856\" height=\"854\" src=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/market-tested@2x.jpg\" class=\"hover-card__figure__image\" alt=\"Intersection\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/market-tested@2x.jpg 856w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/market-tested@2x-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/market-tested@2x-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/market-tested@2x-768x766.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 856px) 100vw, 856px\" \/><div class=\"hover-card__duotone\"><\/div><div class=\"hover-card__overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"hover-card__gradient\"><\/div><\/figure><div class=\"hover-card__arrow\"><svg class=\"hover-card__arrow__image\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 18.938 10.992\"><path d=\"M25.859,20.328l-5.5,5.5V21.336H6.922V19.309H20.363l.012-4.477Z\" transform=\"translate(-6.921 -14.832)\"\/><\/svg><\/div><div class=\"hover-card__front\"><h2 class=\"hover-card__title\">Market Tested<\/h2><h3 class=\"hover-card__subtitle\">Insights you can trust<\/h3><p class=\"hover-card__description\">For nearly three decades, we have leveraged data, analyzed markets, identified efficiencies, and found value where others weren\u2019t looking. We have built a consistent track record of using data and insights to build businesses that seek to unlock this value for investors and residents. There is tremendous potential to scale as we leverage the power of the Amherst platform to grow our current businesses and scan the horizon for the next opportunities.<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n<div id=\"stats\" class=\"block dots-home-stats-top-left dots-home-stats-bottom-right dots-home-stats-inner-block none\"><div class=\"block__inner\">\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center leading-title\">BY THE NUMBERS<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div id=\"stats-block_a532e9ae17a4ede9c1f3357414106494\" class=\"stats\"><ul class=\"stats-list\"><li class=\"stats-list__item\"><span class=\"stats-list__item__number\">$18.5B<\/span><span class=\"stats-list__item__label\">Assets Under Management<\/span><\/li><li class=\"stats-list__item\"><span class=\"stats-list__item__number\">32<\/span><span class=\"stats-list__item__label\">U.S. Markets<\/span><\/li><li class=\"stats-list__item\"><span class=\"stats-list__item__number\">45,000+<\/span><span class=\"stats-list__item__label\">Homes Under Management<\/span><\/li><\/ul><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center footnote\">As of December 31, 2023<\/p>\n\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n<div id=\"big-thinking\" class=\"block padding-bottom none\"><div class=\"block__inner\">\n<style>\r@media screen and (min-width: 1440px) { \r#image-cluster-one-text-block_e110e203e23f8868b6146a6b02ecd757 .image-text__image {grid-column: 6 \/ span 7 ;}\r\r#image-cluster-one-text-block_e110e203e23f8868b6146a6b02ecd757 .image-text__text {grid-column: 1 \/ span 5 ;}\r }<\/style><section id=\"image-cluster-one-text-block_e110e203e23f8868b6146a6b02ecd757\" class=\"image-text\" data-id=\"block_e110e203e23f8868b6146a6b02ecd757\"><div class=\"image-text__image\"><figure class=\"image-cluster-one inview\"><div class=\"image-cluster-one__one\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"478\" height=\"628\" src=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/house-sunset@2x.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"House sunset behind tree\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/house-sunset@2x.jpg 478w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/house-sunset@2x-228x300.jpg 228w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 478px) 100vw, 478px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"image-cluster-one__two\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"767\" height=\"628\" src=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/woman-crossing-arms@2x.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Woman standing confidently crossing arms and smiling\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/woman-crossing-arms@2x.jpg 767w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/woman-crossing-arms@2x-300x246.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 767px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"image-cluster-one__three\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1289\" height=\"634\" src=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/austin-congress-ave@2x.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Looking down Congress Ave at buildings and capitol building in Austin, Tx\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/austin-congress-ave@2x.jpg 1289w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/austin-congress-ave@2x-300x148.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/austin-congress-ave@2x-1024x504.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.amherst.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/austin-congress-ave@2x-768x378.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1289px) 100vw, 1289px\" \/><\/div><\/figure><\/div><div class=\"image-text__text\">\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading h1\" id=\"big-thinking\"><meta charset=\"utf-8\">Big <em>Thinking<\/em><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We are a team of creative problem solvers with a Texas-sized imagination of what is possible. Our sophisticated market insights, precise execution capabilities, and entrepreneurial approach transform \u2018moonshots\u2019 into realities.<\/p>\n\n\n<div id=\"button-block_fb9e8530e5d00f170a75b9c26dde7eeb\" class=\"button-block left\"><div class=\"button-block__inner\"><a href=\"\/firm\/\" title=\"View\" class=\"button-block__link button-block__link--text\">Firm<span class=\"button-block__link__arrow\"><svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 10\"><path d=\"M5,0l5,8H0Z\" transform=\"translate(8) rotate(90)\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/section>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n<div id=\"research\" class=\"block padding-bottom light-gray\"><div class=\"block__inner\">\n<div id=\"feat-news-posts-block_d9af44c72c060491f07a794c80442293\" class=\"feat-news-posts\"><div class=\"feat-news-posts__top\"><h2 class=\"h1\">Research <em>&amp; Insights<\/em><\/h2><div class=\"feat-news-posts__top__link\"><a href=\"\/insights\/\" title=\"View\" class=\"button-block__link button-block__link--text\">View More<span class=\"button-block__link__arrow\"><svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 8 10\"><path d=\